he work, and these have not been transfered to a third party OR&l;/li&g;&l;li&g;the work has already been published under a Creative Commons/open source license and therefore requires the same licensing.&l;/li&g;&l;/ul&g; Please also bear in mind: &l;ul&g;&l;li&g;Creative Commons and open source licenses cannot be revoked or changed.&l;/li&g;&l;li&g;When licensing software, authorization must be obtained from ETH transfer.&l;/li&g;&l;li&g;If possible, the license should be integrated into the work.&l;/li&g;&l;/ul&g; Please select the desired license from the dropdown menu. If you do not wish to issue an end-user license, please select &l;i&g;In Copyright - Non-Commercial Use Permitted&l;/i&g;.&l;/div&g;&q;,&q;form.ethzlicense.input.no-license&q;:&q;No license&q;,&q;form.ethzlicense.input.placeholder&q;:&q;Select a license...&q;,&q;submission.sections.submit.progressbar.describe.ethzlicense&q;:&q;Enduser License&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isEditorOfPublication&q;:&q;Editor&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isContactPersonOfPublication&q;:&q;Contact Person&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isDataCollectorOfPublication&q;:&q;Data Collector&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isProducerOfPublication&q;:&q;Producer&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isProjectLeaderOfPublication&q;:&q;Project Leader&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isProjectManagerOfPublication&q;:&q;Project Manager&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isProjectMemberOfPublication&q;:&q;Project Member&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isRelatedPersonOfPublication&q;:&q;Related Person&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isResearcherOfPublication&q;:&q;Researcher&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isResearchGroupOfPublication&q;:&q;Research Group&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isRightsHolderOfPublication&q;:&q;Rights Holder&q;,&q;item.page.relationships.isOtherOfPublication&q;:&q;Contributor&q;,&q;item.page.ethz-grant&q;:&q;Funding&q;,&q;atmire.submission.search-modal.title.ethz.grant&q;:&q;Search for Projects / Grants&q;,&q;default-relationships-ethz.search.results.head&q;:&q;Search Results&q;,&q;error.validation.datavolumerequired&q;:&q;Data volume is required for large data volume uploads&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataAccess.hint&q;:&q;With libdrive research data can only be published open access. If you need an embargo before publication please send us an e-mail: &l;a href=&s;mailto:{{email}}&s;&g;{{email}}&l;/a&g;&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataAccess.openAccess&q;:&q;Open access&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataAccess.title&q;:&q;Data access&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.checkbox&q;:&q;Upload large data volumes (files &g; 10 GB, items &g; 50 GB total)&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.hint&q;:&q;Please specify the volume of research data you would like to publish. We will allocate the required disc space on the server.&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.info&q;:&q;Large data can be published using our platform libdrive. The data will be linked to the item in the Research Collection. To receive an upload link please fill in the form below and complete your submission. For more information please consult the &l;a href=&s;{{manualRoute}}&s; target=&s;_blank&s;&g;manual&l;/a&g;&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.info-alert&q;:&q;Only files up to 10 GB can be uploaded for a total of 50 GB per item. If you have more data, please select the following checkbox&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.label&q;:&q;Data volume in GB: *&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.dataVolume.placeholder&q;:&q;Enter the volume&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.longTerm.checkbox&q;:&q;I want my data to be reusable for a long time (more than 10 years)&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.longTerm.hint&q;:&q;If you select this option, we will evaluate the long term usability of your data and suggest measures if necessary (e.g. converting files to different formats). More information can be found in our &l;a href=&s;{{manualRoute}}&s; target=&s;_blank&s;&g;manual&l;/a&g;&q;,&q;submission.sections.libdrive-upload.longTerm.label&q;:&q;Ensure long-term usability:&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isEditorOfPublication&q;:&q;Selected Editors&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isSupervisorOfPublication&q;:&q;Selected Supervisors&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isAuthorOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Authors&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isContactPersonOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Contact People&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isDataCollectorOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Data Collectors&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isProducerOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Producers&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isProjectLeaderOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Project Leaders&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isProjectManagerOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Project Managers&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isProjectMemberOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Project Members&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isRelatedPersonOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Related People&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isResearcherOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Researchers&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isResearchGroupOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Researcher Groups&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isRightsHolderOfResearchData&q;:&q;Selected Rights Holders&q;,&q;submission.sections.describe.relationship-lookup.selection-tab.title.isOtherOfResearchData&q;:&q;