id&q;:&q;Your ORCID iD:&q;,&q;assignOrcid.tabTitle&q;:&q;Assign author profile&q;,&q;assignOrcid.breadcrumbs&q;:&q;Assign author profile&q;,&q;orcid.assign.assign.current.user&q;:&q;Claim publications&q;,&q;orcid.assign.dismiss&q;:&q;Dismiss&q;,&q;orcid.assign.dismissed-button.include&q;:&q;Include dismissed items&q;,&q;orcid.assign.dismissed-button.exclude&q;:&q;Exclude dismissed items&q;,&q;assign-orcid.search-button&q;:&q;Search&q;,&q;assign-orcid.no-items-selected&q;:&q;No items selected&q;,&q;assign-orcid.no-items-selected.body&q;:&q;Please select at least one item to process&q;,&q;assign-orcid.no-person-match.alert&q;:&q;No records found with the specified ORCID iD. Please check if your ORCID iD is linked to your ETH profile. Once your ORCID iD is linked, please perform the assigning again the following day. If you have any questions, please contact research-collection@library.ethz.ch&q;,&q;assign-orcid.single-person-match.alert&q;:&q;Linking to current user will create a relationship between the selected item(s) and the Person entity item associated with current user&q;,&q;assign-orcid.multiple-person-match.alert.part1&q;:&q;Multiple records have been found with this ORCID iD. Please contact research-collection@library.ethz.ch&q;,&q;assign-orcid.multiple-person-match.alert.search-link-part&q;:&q;See this search&q;,&q;assign-orcid.introduction.head&q;:&q;Introduction&q;,&q;assign-orcid.introduction.text&q;:&q;Use the checkboxes to select an item and its associated contributor field and then use the “Claim publications” button to assign your author profile to the selected item(s). This will: &l;ul&g;&l;li&g;update your author/contributor name in the item’s metadata with your prefered author name as specified in your ETH person profile.&l;/li&g;&l;li&g;make your name clickable on the item&s;s landing page, linking to your person profile which shows your full name and name variants&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;have your ORCID iD associated with this selected item.&l;/li&g;&